  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nTrinity currently doesn't use different databases for `full` and `light` mode. It should as toggling between these modes will yield unexpected results with a shared database\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nAdd a suffix to the `database-dir` part of the path.\r\n\r\n- `~/.local/share/trinity/mainnet/light-chain/`\r\n- `~/.local/share/trinity/mainnet/full-chain/`\r\n\r\nThis will need to be done in the `trinity.utils.chain.ChainConfig`\r\n",
